These is the original readme file for the Push extension.

Extension page on mediawiki.org: https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Push
Latest version of the readme file: https://github.com/wikimedia/mediawiki-extensions-Push/blob/master/README

== About ==

The Push extension is a simple lightweight tool that adds an extra tab to articles which
enables users to push the content of the article to one or more other MediaWiki wikis.
